---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact & Réservation" activeNav="contact" description="Contactez la Résidence Les Sirènes G&B à Lambaréné pour réserver votre chambre ou suite. Route de Fougamou, Quartier Atsié.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero" style="background-image:url('/images/aerien.jpg'); background-size:cover; background-position:center;">
    <div class="page-hero-bg" style="background:none;"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <span class="eyebrow">Contact & Réservation</span>
      <h1>Réservez<br /><em>votre séjour</em></h1>
      <div class="waves">〰〰〰</div>
      <p>Nous répondons à toutes vos demandes dans les meilleurs délais.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT INFO + FORM -->
  <section class="section-contact">
    <div class="container contact-grid">

      <!-- LEFT: Infos -->
      <div class="contact-info reveal">
        <div class="info-block">
          <h2>Nous Contacter</h2>
          <div class="gold-divider" style="margin-left:0; max-width:150px"><span>〰</span></div>
          <p>Pour réserver votre chambre ou suite, organiser une excursion ou simplement nous poser une question, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter par téléphone ou email.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-cards">
          <div class="contact-card">
            <div class="cc-icon">📞</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Téléphone</h4>
              <a href="tel:+24166050741">+241 66 05 07 41</a>
              <a href="tel:+24177530556">+241 77 53 05 56</a>
              <a href="tel:+24174427474">+241 74 42 74 74</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-card">
            <div class="cc-icon">✉️</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Email</h4>
              <a href="mailto:infosirene@yahoo.fr">infosirene@yahoo.fr</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-card">
            <div class="cc-icon">📍</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Adresse</h4>
              <p>Route de Fougamou<br />Quartier Atsié, Lambaréné<br />Gabon</p>
              <p style="margin-top:0.4rem; font-size:0.8rem; opacity:0.6">BP 10, Lambaréné</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-card">
            <div class="cc-icon">🕐</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Réception</h4>
              <p>Ouverte 7j/7<br />24h/24</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- TARIFS RAPIDES -->
        <div class="quick-rates">
          <h4>Tarifs indicatifs</h4>
          <div class="rates-grid">
            <div class="rate-item">
              <span>🛏️ Chambre classique</span>
              <strong>35 500 FCFA</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="rate-item">
              <span>🌟 Suite avec salon</span>
              <strong>70 500 FCFA</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="rate-item">
              <span>🍽️ Repas moyen</span>
              <strong>15 000 FCFA</strong>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: Form -->
      <div class="contact-form-wrap reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s">
        <div class="form-header">
          <h3>Formulaire de Réservation</h3>
          <p>Complétez ce formulaire et nous vous répondrons rapidement.</p>
        </div>

        <form class="contact-form" id="reservationForm">
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="prenom">Prénom</label>
              <input type="text" id="prenom" name="prenom" placeholder="Votre prénom" required />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="nom">Nom</label>
              <input type="text" id="nom" name="nom" placeholder="Votre nom" required />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="votre@email.com" required />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="telephone">Téléphone</label>
            <input type="tel" id="telephone" name="telephone" placeholder="+241 XX XX XX XX" />
          </div>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="arrivee">Date d'arrivée</label>
              <input type="date" id="arrivee" name="arrivee" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="depart">Date de départ</label>
              <input type="date" id="depart" name="depart" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="type-chambre">Type d'hébergement</label>
            <select id="type-chambre" name="type-chambre">
              <option value="">Choisir un hébergement</option>
              <option value="chambre-classique">Chambre Classique (35 500 FCFA)</option>
              <option value="suite">Suite avec Salon (70 500 FCFA)</option>
              <option value="restaurant">Réservation restaurant uniquement</option>
              <option value="excursion">Excursion / Activité</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="voyageurs">Nombre de voyageurs</label>
            <select id="voyageurs" name="voyageurs">
              <option value="1">1 personne</option>
              <option value="2" selected>2 personnes</option>
              <option value="3">3 personnes</option>
              <option value="4">4 personnes et plus</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Message / Demandes spéciales</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Demandes particulières, questions sur les activités, allergies alimentaires..."></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn-primary form-submit">
            Envoyer ma demande
          </button>

          <p class="form-note">
            * Ce formulaire envoie directement une demande à notre équipe.<br />
            Nous vous répondons par email ou téléphone sous 24h.
          </p>
        </form>

        <div class="form-success" id="formSuccess" style="display:none">
          <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
          <h3>Demande envoyée !</h3>
          <p>Merci pour votre message. Notre équipe vous contactera dans les meilleurs délais.</p>
          <p>Pour une réponse rapide, appelez-nous directement :</p>
          <a href="tel:+24166050741" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:1rem; display:inline-block">📞 +241 66 05 07 41</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CARTE / LOCALISATION -->
  <section class="section-map section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--or-sable)">Localisation</span>
        <h2 style="color:var(--creme-ecru)">Nous Trouver à Lambaréné</h2>
        <div class="gold-divider"><span>〰</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="map-content reveal">
        <div class="map-frame">
          <div class="map-visual">
            <div class="map-pin">📍</div>
            <p class="map-name">Résidence Les Sirènes G&B</p>
            <p class="map-addr">Route de Fougamou, Quartier Atsié</p>
            <p class="map-city">Lambaréné, Gabon</p>
            <div class="map-coords">Lac Mbolet • Fleuve Ogooué</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="map-directions">
          <h3>Comment nous rejoindre</h3>
          <div class="directions-list">
            <div class="direction-item">
              <span class="dir-icon">✈️</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Par avion</strong>
                <p>L'aéroport de Lambaréné (LBQ) est la porte d'entrée principale. Des vols réguliers depuis Libreville (45 min).</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="direction-item">
              <span class="dir-icon">🚗</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Par route</strong>
                <p>Depuis Libreville via la N1 : environ 3-4h. La résidence est sur la Route de Fougamou, dans le Quartier Atsié.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="direction-item">
              <span class="dir-icon">🛶</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Par voie d'eau</strong>
                <p>Possibilité d'arriver en pirogue depuis certains points du fleuve Ogooué. Nous contacter pour l'organisation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="address-block">
            <h4>Adresse postale</h4>
            <p>BP 10, Lambaréné, Gabon</p>
            <p>Route de Fougamou, Quartier Atsié</p>
            <div class="address-phones">
              <a href="tel:+24166050741">📞 +241 66 05 07 41</a>
              <a href="tel:+24177530556">📞 +241 77 53 05 56</a>
              <a href="tel:+24174427474">📞 +241 74 42 74 74</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('reservationForm') as HTMLFormElement;
  const success = document.getElementById('formSuccess');

  form?.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    if (form && success) {
      form.style.display = 'none';
      success.style.display = 'block';
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    min-height: 55vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #061525 0%, #0A233C 60%, #0d2d4a 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .page-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(195,155,65,0.07), transparent);
  }

  .page-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    color: var(--creme-ecru);
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease both;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-modern);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--or-sable);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-hero-content h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-titre);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-hero-content h1 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--or-sable);
  }

  .waves {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--or-sable);
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .page-hero-content p {
    color: rgba(245,240,230,0.75);
    max-width: 450px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* CONTACT SECTION */
  .section-contact {
    padding: var(--section-pad);
    background: var(--sable-fin);
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .info-block h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--bleu-abyssal);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .info-block p {
    color: #5a6a7a;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 1.2rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(195,155,65,0.12);
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  .contact-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(10,35,60,0.08);
  }

  .cc-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bleu-abyssal);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .contact-card a,
  .contact-card p {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: #5a6a7a;
    text-decoration: none;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .contact-card a:hover {
    color: var(--or-sable);
  }

  .quick-rates {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(195,155,65,0.25);
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(195,155,65,0.04), transparent);
  }

  .quick-rates h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--or-sable);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .rates-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .rate-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(195,155,65,0.1);
    color: var(--bleu-abyssal);
  }

  .rate-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .rate-item strong {
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    color: var(--or-sable);
  }

  /* FORM */
  .contact-form-wrap {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(195,155,65,0.15);
    padding: 3rem;
  }

  .form-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(195,155,65,0.15);
  }

  .form-header h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--bleu-abyssal);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .form-header p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: #8899aa;
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .form-group label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bleu-abyssal);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .form-group input,
  .form-group select,
  .form-group textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(10,35,60,0.15);
    background: var(--sable-fin);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--bleu-abyssal);
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
  }

  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group select:focus,
  .form-group textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--or-sable);
    background: white;
  }

  .form-group textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 100px;
  }

  .form-submit {
    width: 100%;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .form-note {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #aaa;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .form-success {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
  }

  .success-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .form-success h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--bleu-abyssal);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .form-success p {
    color: #5a6a7a;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* MAP */
  .section-map {
    padding: var(--section-pad);
  }

  .map-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .map-frame {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10,35,60,0.8), rgba(13,58,46,0.8));
    border: 2px solid rgba(195,155,65,0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .map-frame::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 15px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(195,155,65,0.1);
  }

  .map-visual {
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .map-pin {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    animation: bounce 2s ease infinite;
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
  }

  .map-name {
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--creme-ecru);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .map-addr {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,230,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .map-city {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,230,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .map-coords {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--or-sable);
    border: 1px solid rgba(195,155,65,0.3);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .map-directions h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--creme-ecru);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .directions-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .direction-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .dir-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 35px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .direction-item strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--creme-ecru);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .direction-item p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,230,0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .address-block {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(195,155,65,0.2);
    background: rgba(195,155,65,0.05);
  }

  .address-block h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-cinzel);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--or-sable);
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .address-block p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,230,0.7);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .address-phones {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .address-phones a {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--or-sable);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .address-phones a:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .contact-grid,
    .map-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .contact-form-wrap { padding: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
